1. *Smrću* se ne treba igrati. (Do not play with *death*.)
2. Žalim zbog *smrti* tvog oca. (I'm sorry for your father's *death*.)
3. Njegova majka je umrla *smrću* prirodnom uzrokovanom starošću. (His mother died a natural *death* caused by old age.)
4. Tuga i *smrt* su sastavni deo života. (Grief and *death* are an integral part of life.)
5. Njegova želja da umre *smrću* junaka bila je ispunjena. (His desire to die a hero's *death* was fulfilled.)
6. Nisam se plašila *smrti* sve dok nisam postala majka. (I wasn't afraid of *death* until I became a mother.)
7. *Smrću* mu je bila okončana karijera. (His career was ended by *death*.)
8. Ona je prošla kroz težak period nakon *smrti* muža. (She went through a tough time after her husband's *death*.)
9. *Smrću* se ne može manipulisati. (You can't manipulate *death*.)
10. Njegova smrt je izazvala veliku *smućenost* u javnosti. (His death caused a great *commotion* in the public.)